📚 Book Library

A full-stack Book Library application for managing a personal collection of books. Users can securely sign up and sign in, browse their book collection, add new books, update existing books, delete books, and upload book cover images.

The application is built with a React frontend and an ASP.NET Core 8 Web API, with AWS Cognito handling authentication and Amazon S3 providing object storage for book cover images.

✨ Features
🔐 User registration and authentication
🔄 Access token refresh
🚪 Secure sign-out and token revocation
📚 View all books
🔍 Search and browse books
➕ Add new books
✏️ Edit existing books
🗑️ Delete books
🖼️ Upload book cover images
☁️ Store book covers in Amazon S3
🔗 Generate temporary S3 pre-signed URLs for book covers
🛡️ Protect book endpoints with JWT authentication
🗄️ Store book information in SQL Server
📖 Swagger/OpenAPI API documentation
⚡ AWS Lambda-compatible ASP.NET Core API
